HEADWORD: Italicize
<hw>I*tal"i*cize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Italicized</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>;
